        "image": "shopify://shop_images/home.jpg",
        "details": "<p>You can use our Glass Bottle For Life over and over again meaning you never have to throw away your empty plastic bottles every time your cleaner runs out. We have already helped stop 250,000 plastic bottles from going into landfill. Plus, the reusable glass bottle is 100% recyclable so you don’t have to worry about adding more trash to landfills or oceans.</p>",
