        "image": "shopify://shop_images/human.jpg",
        "details": "<p>Generic Surface Cleaners are made of 90% water and over 1 billion of these heavy bottles are transported around the world every year to get to our homes. Purdy & Figg Eco-Concentrates are 97% lighter than a bulk cleaner to ship and you dilute the concentrates with water coming out of your tap at home.</p>",
